:::Child had a dream. There were several bots all crucified in a circle 
around him. a bot, with a pitch black cloak covering him came up to child and 
crucified him. hanging there on a cross child felt his life waist away.  he 
looked up and floating there was an angel, an organic angel, it spoke:::

fear not child this is only a dream,I am here to give you something

:::The angel held out his hand to revile a chalice of iron:::

This is the cup of life, the most sacred item on the face of the planet earth

:::Child reached out and took the cup. then he woke up, with the cup, still 
in his hands:::

:::Child got up and looked at everyone:::

Child; "Al right, every one in the ships! we have to visit the maximals!"

:::Child, Tran, Talin, Herald, Data, and Defection got on the ships. Child 
was still holding the iron cup:::
